          "en": "Q1 2026 EBITDA turned positive (KRW 10bn) for the first time in 10 quarters, led by record semiconductor materials operating profit (KRW 23.6bn, OPM 34.5%) and a surprise chemical segment profit (KRW 9.6bn)"
