          "en": "Successful KRW 1.17 trillion rights offering (issue price KRW 99,500/share): KRW 589.6bn earmarked for Absolics and KRW 577.5bn for debt repayment, expected to slash the debt-to-equity ratio from ~230% to ~129%"
